Deployed Windows 10 Client VM
VM Specs

OS : Windows 10 Pro
RAM : 4 GB
CPU : 2 vCPUs
Disk : 50 GB
Network : Internal Network (labnet)

IP Configuration

IP address : 192.168.10.100
Subnet mask : 255.255.255.0
Default gateway : 192.168.10.254
DNS : 192.168.10.1

Steps

Created VM in VirtualBox with above specs
Mounted Windows 10 ISO and completed installation
Set network adapter to Internal Network (labnet)
Set static IP address manually
Confirmed connectivity to pfSense gateway (ping 192.168.10.254)
Confirmed DNS resolution via Windows Server (ping google.com)

Troubleshooting

No internet initially — fixed by setting default gateway to 192.168.10.254 (pfSense) and DNS to 192.168.10.1 (Windows Server)
